TEXT.S: Anthony Brown Anthony Brown hya'ga NBA pgnaw' mari' misuw qaniy, qutux sa p'agal tins' tay suruw praw maki' tayglaing. kawas tay 1992, ryax sa tay 10 nqu tay 10, Anthony Brown, squliq na p'unro. pinqbaqan nya Anthony Brown mqwas biru sa Ocean View pqwsan biru seneng.
